help_lines=Operit2 TUI\n\nTab: complete command / switch focus\nEnter: send message / activate selected chat\nF3 or /switch: toggle chat list\n/resume: resume previous chat\nUp/Down: select chat when chat list is focused\nCtrl+J: insert newline in input\nCtrl+N: create new chat\nCtrl+C: press twice to quit\nCtrl+Q: quit\nPageUp/PageDown: scroll conversation by page\nCtrl+U/Ctrl+D: scroll conversation by half page\nCtrl+Home/Ctrl+End: top / bottom conversation\nQueue focus: Up/Down select | Enter/s send | e edit | Delete remove\nEsc: cancel request / close help / clear status\n\nLocal commands:\n/help\n/new [--character <name>] [--group-card <id>] [--group <name>]\n/switch\n/resume\n/max\n/language [en|zh-CN]\n/model current | /model list | /model choose\n/model use <provider-id> <model-id>\n/approval | /approval list|allow|ask|forbid\n/approval tool <tool> <allow|ask|forbid|clear>\n/queue | /queue clear|delete|edit|send\n/attach <path>\n/attachments\n/clear-attachments\n/quit\n/character | /character choose\n/group | /group choose\n/skill | /skill toggle\n/package | /package toggle\n/plugin | /plugin toggle\n/mcp | /mcp toggle\n/tag\n/update
